title: Teams we feel differently about
itunes:title: Teams we feel differently about
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – review the latest headlines around the league including the Steelers signing of Mike Vick, Orlando Scandrick's injury and Evan Mathis' decision to sign with the Broncos. The guys then list teams that will leave room for doubt or instill faith after preseason performances.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
